## List Groups

List all groups on your Metting account.

> Definition

```shell
POST <%= config[:api_host] %>group/list
```

```javascript
Metting.group.list();
```

> Example Request

```shell
$ curl <%= config[:api_host] %>group/list \
    -X POST \
    -d api_key=<%= config[:ex_api_key] %> \
    -d api_secret=<%= config[:ex_api_secret] %>
```

```javascript
<%= config[:ex_node_init] %>

Metting.group.list(<%= config[:ex_node_res] %>);
```

> Example Response

```json
{
  "total_records": 1,
  "groups": [
    {
      "group_id": "<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>",
      "account_id": "<%= config[:ex_uuid] %>",
      "name": "Group Test1",
      "total_members": 40
    }
  ]
}
```

